  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. In a bowl, mix softened mascarpone cheese with granulated sugar and vanilla extract.",
    "3. Arrange crisp in a baking dish, adding melted butter to coat.",
    "4. Top crisp with mascarpone mixture and drizzle with tadka (if using).",
    "5. Bake for 20-25 minutes or until the crisp is golden brown.",
    "6. Remove from oven and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "7. Serve warm, topped with additional crisp if desired."
